#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:327
msgid "Rescue Mount"
msgstr "Rescue Mount"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:349
msgid ""
"Your system had dirty file systems which you chose not to mount.  From a "
"shell, you can fsck and mount your partitions manually.\n"
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານມີລະບົບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ບໍ່ສະອາດ (dirty file systems) ເຊິ່ງທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະບໍ່ mount. ທ່ານສາມາດ"
"ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ fsck ແລະ mount ພາທິຊັນຂອງທ່ານເອງໄດ້ຜ່ານ shell.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:358
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your system has been mounted under %(mountpoint)s.\n"
"\n"
"If you would like to make your system the root environment, run the "
"command:\n"
"\n"
"\tchroot %(mountpoint)s\n"
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານຖືກ mount ໄວ້ທີ່ %(mountpoint)s.\n"
"\n"
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານເປັນ root environment, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ:\n"
"\n"
"\tchroot %(mountpoint)s\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:397
#, python-format
msgid "Run %s to unmount the system when you are finished.\n"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ %s ເພື່ອ unmount ລະບົບເມື່ອທ່ານເຮັດວຽກສຳເລັດແລ້ວ.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:399
#, python-format
msgid ""
"An error occurred trying to mount some or all of your system.  Some of it "
"may be mounted under %s\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນການພະຍາຍາມ mount ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານບາງສ່ວນ ຫຼື ທັງໝົດ. ບາງສ່ວນອາດຈະຖືກ mount ໄວ້ທີ່ "
"%s\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:406
msgid "You don't have any Linux partitions.  Rebooting.\n"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ມີພາທິຊັນ Linux ເລີຍ. ກຳລັງເລີ່ມລະບົບໃໝ່.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:413
msgid "The system will reboot automatically when you exit from the shell.\n"
msgstr "ລະບົບຈະເລີ່ມໃໝ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເມື່ອທ່ານອອກຈາກ shell.\n"

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:417
