#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:72
msgid ""
"The 'swap' area on your computer is used by the operating\n"
"system when running low on memory."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'swap' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານຖືກໃຊ້ໂດຍລະບົບ\n"
"ປະຕິບັດການເມື່ອໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳເຫຼືອໜ້ອຍ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:74
msgid ""
"The 'boot' area on your computer is where files needed\n"
"to start the operating system are stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'boot' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນເກັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈຳເປັນ\n"
"ໃນການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:76
msgid ""
"The 'root' area on your computer is where core system\n"
"files and applications are stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'root' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນເກັບໄຟລ໌ລະບົບຫຼັກ\n"
"ແລະ ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນຕ່າງໆ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:78
msgid ""
"The 'home' area on your computer is where all your personal\n"
"data is stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'home' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນທີ່ເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ\n"
"ສ່ວນຕົວຂອງທ່ານທັງໝົດ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:80
msgid ""
"The BIOS boot partition is required to enable booting\n"
"from GPT-partitioned disks on BIOS hardware."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີພາຕິຊັນ BIOS boot ເພື່ອເປີດການບູດ\n"
"ຈາກດິສກ໌ທີ່ແບ່ງແບບ GPT ໃນຮາດແວ BIOS."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:82
msgid ""
"The PReP boot partition is required as part of the\n"
"boot loader configuration on some PPC platforms."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີພາຕິຊັນ PReP boot ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງ\n"
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວໂຫຼດບູດໃນບາງແພລັດຟອມ PPC."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:159
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your root partition is less than %(size)s which is usually too small to "
"install %(product)s."
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນຮາກ (root) ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວນ້ອຍເກີນໄປທີ່ຈະຕິດຕັ້ງ %"
"(product)s."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:165
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not defined a root partition (/), which is required for "
"installation of %s to continue."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດພາຕິຊັນຮາກ (root) (/), ເຊິ່ງຈຳເປັນສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %s ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:178
#, python-format
msgid "Your root partition must be on a device of type: %s."
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນ root ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງອຸປະກອນປະເພດ: %s."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:194
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is less than %(size)s which is lower than "
"recommended for a normal %(productName)s install."
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງຕ່ຳກວ່າຂະໜາດທີ່ແນະນຳສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %"
"(productName)s ປົກກະຕິ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:202
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is less than %(size)s which is lower than required."
msgstr ""
"ພາທິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານມີຂະໜາດໜ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງຕ່ຳກວ່າທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:220
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too small for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %"
"(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:226
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too large for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %"
"(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:245
msgid "No valid boot loader target device found. See below for details."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບອຸປະກອນເປົ້າໝາຍສຳລັບຕົວໂຫຼດບູດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:260
msgid "You have not created a bootable partition."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ສ້າງພາຕິຊັນທີ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:295
msgid ""
"Your BIOS-based system needs a special partition to boot from a GPT disk "
"label. To continue, please create a 1MiB 'biosboot' type partition."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບທີ່ອີງໃສ່ BIOS ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງການພາຕິຊັນພິເສດເພື່ອບູດຈາກປ້າຍຊື່ດິສກ໌ GPT. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່, ກະລຸນາສ້"
"າງພາຕິຊັນປະເພດ 'biosboot' ຂະໜາດ 1MiB."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:316
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. %(requiredMem)s of memory is "
"required to continue installation without a swap partition, but you only "
"have %(installedMem)s."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(requiredMem)s ເພື່ອສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງໂດຍບໍ່ມີພ"
"າຕິຊັນ swap, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(installedMem)s."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:322
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. Although not strictly required in "
"all cases, it will significantly improve performance for most installations."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າມັນຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ບັງຄັບໃນທຸກກໍລະນີ, ແຕ່ມັນຈະປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼ"
"າຍສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນໃຫຍ່."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:340
msgid ""
"At least one of your swap devices does not have a UUID, which is common in "
"swap space created using older versions of mkswap. These devices will be "
"referred to by device path in /etc/fstab, which is not ideal since device "
"paths can change under a variety of circumstances. "
msgstr ""
"ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໃນອຸປະກອນ swap ຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບໍ່ມີ UUID, ເຊິ່ງເປັນເລື່ອງປົກກະຕິສຳລັບພື້ນທີ່ swap ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນມາໂ"
"ດຍໃຊ້ mkswap ລຸ້ນເກົ່າ. ອຸປະກອນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກອ້າງອີງໂດຍເສັ້ນທາງອຸປະກອນ (device path) ໃນ /etc/"
"fstab, ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ເໝາະສົມປານໃດ ເພາະເສັ້ນທາງອຸປະກອນສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ໃນຫຼາຍສະຖານະການ. "

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:361
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This mount point is invalid. The %s directory must be on the / file system."
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ %s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງ/ລະບົບໄຟລ໌."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:377
#, python-format
msgid "Your %s must be on a separate partition or LV."
msgstr "%s ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງພາທິຊັນ ຫຼື LV ທີ່ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:394
#, python-format
msgid "The mount point %s must be on a linux file system."
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ %s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ Linux."

#: pyanaconda/storage_utils.py:413
#, python-format
msgid "LUKS device %s has no encryption key"
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນ LUKS %s ບໍ່ມີຄີຖອດລະຫັດ"

#: pyanaconda/users.py:234
#, python-format
msgid "User name is reserved for system: %s"
msgstr "ຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຖືກສະຫງວນໄວ້ສຳລັບລະບົບ: %s"

#: pyanaconda/users.py:237
msgid "User name cannot start with '-' character"
msgstr "ຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ '-' ໄດ້"

#: pyanaconda/users.py:246
#, python-format
msgid "User name cannot contain character: '%s'"
msgstr "ຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ບໍ່ສາມາດມີຕົວອັກສອນ: '%s'"

#: pyanaconda/users.py:249
msgid "User name must be shorter than 33 characters"
msgstr "ຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງສັ້ນກວ່າ 33 ຕົວອັກສອນ"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:76
#, python-format
msgid "%(productName)s %(productVersion)s installation"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(productName)s %(productVersion)s"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:139
#, python-format
msgid "%(productName)s %(productVersion)s installation on host %(name)s"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(productName)s %(productVersion)s ຢູ່ເທິງໂຮສ %(name)s"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:158
#, python-format
msgid "Attempting to connect to vnc client on host %s..."
msgstr "ກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ vnc client ຢູ່ເທິງໂຮສ %s..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:172
msgid "Connected!"
msgstr "ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແລ້ວ!"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:175
msgid "Will try to connect again in 15 seconds..."
msgstr "ຈະພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ໃນອີກ 15 ວິນາທີ..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:182
#, python-format
msgid "Giving up attempting to connect after %d try!\n"
msgid_plural "Giving up attempting to connect after %d tries!\n"
msgstr[0] "ຍົກເລີກການພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫຼັງຈາກລອງໄປແລ້ວ %d ຄັ້ງ!\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:190
msgid "Attempting to start vncconfig"
msgstr "ກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມເລີ່ມ vncconfig"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:203
#, python-format
msgid "Please manually connect your vnc client to %s to begin the install."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ vnc client ຂອງທ່ານຫາ %s ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເພື່ອເລີ່ມການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:205
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Please manually connect your vnc client to <IP ADDRESS>:%s to begin the "
"install. Switch to the shell (Ctrl-B 2) and run 'ip addr' to find the <IP "
"ADDRESS>."
msgstr ""
"ກະລຸນາເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ vnc client ຂອງທ່ານໄປທີ່ <IP ADDRESS>:%s ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເພື່ອເລີ່ມການຕິດຕັ້ງ. ສະຫຼັບໄປ"
"ທີ່ shell (Ctrl-B 2) ແລ້ວໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ 'ip addr' ເພື່ອເບິ່ງ <IP ADDRESS>."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:210
msgid "Starting VNC..."
msgstr "ກຳລັງເລີ່ມ VNC..."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:247
msgid "The VNC server is now running."
msgstr "ເຊີບເວີ VNC ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:251
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"You chose to connect to a listening vncviewer. \n"
"This does not require a password to be set.  If you \n"
"set a password, it will be used in case the connection \n"
"to the vncviewer is unsuccessful\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ vncviewer ທີ່ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່. \n"
"ນີ້ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງລະຫັດຜ່ານ. ຖ້າທ່ານ \n"
"ຕັ້ງລະຫັດຜ່ານ, ມັນຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ \n"
"ຫາ vncviewer ບໍ່ສຳເລັດ\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:256
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"WARNING!!! VNC server running with NO PASSWORD!\n"
"You can use the vncpassword=<password> boot option\n"
"if you would like to secure the server.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ຄຳເຕືອນ!!! ເຊີບເວີ VNC ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກໂດຍບໍ່ມີລະຫັດຜ່ານ!\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກບູດ vncpassword=<ລະຫັດຜ່ານ>\n"
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຮັດໃຫ້ເຊີບເວີປອດໄພ.\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:260
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"You chose to execute vnc with a password. \n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ vnc ພ້ອມກັບລະຫັດຜ່ານ. \n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:262
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Unknown Error.  Aborting. \n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກ. ກຳລັງຍົກເລີກ. \n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:284
msgid ""
"VNC password must be six to eight characters long.\n"
"Please enter a new one, or leave blank for no password."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດຜ່ານ VNC ຕ້ອງມີຄວາມຍາວແຕ່ 6 ຫາ 8 ຕົວອັກສອນ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາປ້ອນລະຫັດໃໝ່ ຫຼື ປະຫວ່າງໄວ້ຖ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການລະຫັດຜ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/packaging/__init__.py:1374
msgid "Failed to set up installation source"
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າແຫຼ່ງຕິດຕັ້ງບໍ່ສຳເລັດ"

#: pyanaconda/packaging/__init__.py:1375
msgid "Error downloading package metadata"
msgstr "ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນການດາວໂຫຼດເມຕາດາຕາຂອງແພັກເກດ"

#: pyanaconda/packaging/__init__.py:1376
msgid "No installation source available"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນການຕິດຕັ້ງທີ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ"

#: pyanaconda/packaging/livepayload.py:98
#: pyanaconda/packaging/livepayload.py:119
msgid "Installing software"
msgstr "ກຳລັງຕິດຕັ້ງຊອບແວ"

#: pyanaconda/packaging/livepayload.py:220
