"default one) when you decrypt your disks after install."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳເຕືອນ: ທ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດສະຫຼັບຮູບແບບແປ້ນພິມໄດ້ (ຈາກອັນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ) ເມື່ອທ່ານຖອດລະຫັດດິດຂອງທ່ານຫຼັງຈາກກາ"
"ນຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:1
msgid "RESCAN DISKS"
msgstr "ສະແກນດິດໃໝ່"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:2
msgctxt "GUI|Refresh Dialog|Rescan"
msgid "_Cancel"
msgstr "_ຍົກເລີກ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:3
msgctxt "GUI|Refresh Dialog|Rescan"
msgid "_OK"
msgstr "_ຕົກລົງ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:4
msgid ""
"You can remove or insert additional disks at this time and press 'Rescan "
"Disks' below for the changes to take effect."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຖອດ ຫຼື ໃສ່ດິດເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ໃນເວລານີ້ ແລະ ກົດ 'ສະແກນດິດໃໝ່' ດ້ານລຸ່ມເພື່ອໃຫ້ການປ່ຽນແປງມີຜົນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:5
msgid ""
"<b>Warning:</b> All storage changes made using the installer will be lost "
"when you press 'Rescan Disks'."
msgstr ""
"<b>ຄຳເຕືອນ:</b> ການປ່ຽນແປງບ່ອນຈັດເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດທີ່ເຮັດຜ່ານຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງຈະສູນຫາຍໄປເມື່ອທ່ານກົດ 'ສະແກນດິ"
"ດໃໝ່'."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:6
msgctxt "GUI|Refresh Dialog|Rescan"
msgid "_Rescan Disks"
msgstr "ສະແກນດິດໃໝ່(_R)"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:7
msgid "Scanning disks.  This may take a moment..."
msgstr "ກຳລັງສະແກນດິດ. ອາດຈະໃຊ້ເວລາຈັກໜ່ອຍ..."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:8
msgid ""
"You may <a href=\"\">go back to the main menu</a> to complete other\n"
"installation options while this scan completes."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະ <a href=\"\">ກັບໄປທີ່ເມນູຫຼັກ</a> ເພື່ອເຮັດສຳເລັດຕົວເລືອກ\n"
"ການຕິດຕັ້ງອື່ນໆໃນຂະນະທີ່ການສະແກນນີ້ກຳລັງດຳເນີນໄປ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade.h:10
msgid "Disk rescan complete."
msgstr "ການສະແກນດິດໃໝ່ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/resize.glade.h:1
