msgstr "ພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ສາມາດຮຽກຄືນໄດ້"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/resize.glade.h:9
#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/summary.glade.h:6
